{"tid":1308580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(禁止中共代理人) 23網媒「染紅」照抄中国官媒   台灣總統府：證明修法急迫性","createTime":"2019-07-12T02:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T03:03:37.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"66eb6e2a349ad89ca3cdc3257a596a9b02cff573","tid":1308580,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/xXDMxUPDt3tZbtyObwBRIg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/78b98988e7c3cfc091250ea12f2403f4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FxXDMxUPDt3tZbtyObwBRIg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2F78b98988e7c3cfc091250ea12f2403f4&h=0e1dcf2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國國台辦旗下的「中國台灣網」，日前發表批判蔡英文總統的文章，結果23家台灣網媒一字不漏照抄中國官媒的文章，昨（11日）總統府發言人丁允恭表示，紅色滲透證明修法的急迫性。公民記者林雨蒼昨分析後發現，許多網站都是由「指動傳播科技有限公司」所經營，許多網站現已經關閉，他特定將網站Logo做成體系脈絡圖，供台灣民眾參考指認。<br />\n<br />\n針對中國國台辦旗下的「中國台灣網」，日前發表「今日蔡當局霸道拔『管』，明年民眾輕鬆拔『蔡』」文章，被23家台灣網媒全文轉貼。《自由時報》報導稱，總統府發言人丁允恭表示，23家台灣網媒同步照抄中國官媒、對政府不實打擊的現象，證明這樣的威脅確實存在，而且影響甚鉅，「紅色滲透」事件正證明修法的必要性與急迫性。<br />\n<br />\n蔡政府力拚立法院下一個會期要完成「禁止中共代理人」的修法，嚴格規範人民、法人、團體或機構為中共進行危害國安的政治宣傳、發表聲明，參加中共所舉辦的會議。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/MwrGIDIl3L2T5B7L2c5Bdw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-TW/mirrormedia.mg/626112856774f53b6cee762e23c6d615\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FMwrGIDIl3L2T5B7L2c5Bdw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-TW%2Fmirrormedia.mg%2F626112856774f53b6cee762e23c6d615&h=d149649c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，丁允恭說，蔡總統提出要為台灣建構「民主防護網」，正是因應這樣的情勢，政府也已進行一連串的立法工作，如兩岸條例、國安法、國家機密保護法、刑法等法律的修正，阻絕中國透過資本滲透、媒體滲透、網路滲透等手段，擾亂台灣社會，製造社會紛擾，危害民主體制正常運作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B023%E7%B6%B2%E5%AA%92-%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85-%E7%85%A7%E6%8A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92-%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%BA%9C-%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E4%BF%AE%E6%B3%95%E6%80%A5%E8%BF%AB%E6%80%A7-020533726.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%258F%25B023%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%25B4%2585-%25E7%2585%25A7%25E6%258A%2584%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2598%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%25BA%259C-%25E8%25AD%2589%25E6%2598%258E%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E6%2580%25A7-020533726.html&d=tO8FO7ZpCqi602%2BiQgdm0LhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=44d3b2a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8F%B023%E7%B6%B2%E5%AA%92-%E6%9F%93%E7%B4%85-%E7%85%A7%E6%8A%84%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%98%E5%AA%92-%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%BA%9C-%E8%AD%89%E6%98%8E%E4%BF%AE%E6%B3%95%E6%80%A5%E8%BF%AB%E6%80%A7-020533726.html</a>"},{"pid":"cb29ecd1dec74746411fa8c5904d1d4572b75ce6","tid":1308580,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:31:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a6ee2dbbcbe1c233095a913743769c531ffe2b0","tid":1308580,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T02:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc03046bd2ef39fff5a5f8cfd038ee30e74b4fab","tid":1308580,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T03:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}